| blood_type   | enum('A+','A-','B+','B-','AB+','AB-','O+','O-') | NO   |     | NULL                |                |
| role         | enum('donor','seeker')                          | NO   |     | NULL                |                |
| availability | tinyint(1)                                      | YES  |     | 1                   |                |
